title: Ivanka Trump meets with South Korean President Moon Jae-in
text:
Ivanka Trump meets with South Korean President Moon Jae-in 2:34pm GMT - 00:46 
U.S. President Donald Trump's daughter and senior White House adviser, Ivanka Trump, meets with South Korean President Moon Jae-in at Seoul's Blue House. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
